entry.tran: 无最后结果的;无结论的
entry.def: If research or evidence is inconclusive, it has not proved anything.

example.ex: Research has so far proved inconclusive...

entry.tran: (竞赛、冲突)胜负不明的,无最后结果的
entry.def: If a contest or conflict is inconclusive, it is not clear who has won or who is winning.
